{"tid":58264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新北] 73歲老翁收2百元 大馬路旁幫友人口交","createTime":"2016-12-28T16:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T01:49:53.000Z","uid":51183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd24884c35d7c217ead6b20616981d274e02f8dd","tid":58264,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:21:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/1931128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F1931128&d=gJNUPDTSKQV1d5aa5ltafgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=505fadcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F1931128&h=ddbc896e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/1931128</a><br />\n<br />\n扯！73歲老翁收2百元 大馬路旁幫友人口交<br />\n<br />\n2016-12-28  20:20<br />\n<br />\n〔記者王宣晴／新北報導〕高中後門上演活春宮？有民眾深夜行經新北市蘆洲某高中後門時驚見兩名男子在口交，嚇得連忙報案，警方獲報迅速趕抵，將兩人依公然猥褻現行犯帶回，警方訊問時得知其中一名男子已高齡73歲，且收了200元就幫友人口交，直呼就算喝醉也太失序，訊後依法將兩人送辦。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，43歲的顏男及73歲的柯男原先就是友人，本月21日晚間11時許，兩人相約飲酒，並坐在蘆洲民權路58巷口對面的木椅上閒聊，沒想到顏男酒後有些衝動，向柯男表示：「懶叫硬硬的，幫我處理一下」，並拿出2百元，要求柯男幫忙口交，柯男見兩人交情不錯便仗著酒意答應，兩男在大路旁演起活春宮，附近民眾見狀報案。<br />\n<br />\n警方獲報趕抵，兩男還沉浸在情慾世界無法自拔，員警連忙大喝：「你們在幹嘛！分開！」並將兩人帶回，柯男向警方供稱，顏男先問：「我平常對你如何」，因兩人本來就是朋友，所以他回：「無話可說」，隨後在路旁做出失序行為，警方訊後依公然猥褻罪嫌送辦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce1d05d0acfe7b14e8d3916a55274b4fffa1bf8","tid":58264,"uid":41050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:23:59.000Z","msg":"加幾多分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80c4663148a76b32ad9756eceb9cd6b2505e912","tid":58264,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:24:38.000Z","msg":"阿伯仲有冇牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471c214c99953e193ca263eb043686bc7900dcea","tid":58264,"uid":33684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:25:02.000Z","msg":"幫你吹吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f23dee34a3d0f899be22ed6c3e29932c0dbd80e","tid":58264,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:28:26.000Z","msg":"唔識計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9338d07e81359beda957edc561dbc3a51744d43a","tid":58264,"uid":56725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:31:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a29854182660da4d51717eda9b75fb3af0fd373a","tid":58264,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"邊個重口味啲？"},{"pid":"fc9ae289f2464923ca6eb8fffa807c30202d8d51","tid":58264,"uid":66928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:35:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三分當入另再加罰球"},{"pid":"2d363f3626da7933fb943e96be524d5b6fefbd6d","tid":58264,"uid":9789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:54:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫你吹吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌係咪之前裝修個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑撚死"},{"pid":"8206588c3e3a9376914521673b4939a6f3de8ce2","tid":58264,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:55:14.000Z","msg":"仲有冇風化聯賽？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777aced3750a821134cd0aea4b7116610dd8daf5","tid":58264,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:56:41.000Z","msg":"柯男見兩人交情不錯便仗著酒意答應"},{"pid":"46e3d4f65acd4c30f316f0a1aeb6b43